Results for the Referendum of Southern Sudan

Overview
  • 1.17% unity 44,888 votes
  • 98.83% secession 3,792,518 votes
  • Votes cast: 3,851,994
  • Valid votes: 3,837,406
  • Blank votes: 6,222
  • Invalid votes: 8,366
Voter turnout: 97.58%
Results distribution

The results displayed across this website are the final certified results from the Southern Sudan Referendum Commission.

Both the raw data and final reports are freely available for download; download the raw data (CSV) or download the results report (PDF).
